item.title: COCO → labelImg yolo
item.description: One-click conversion of COCO format data to labelImg labeled yolo format data. COCO format directory structure（see dataset/YOLOV5_COCO_format for details）： YOLOV5_COCO_format ├── annotations │ ├── instances_train2017.json │ └── instances_val2017.json ├── train2017 │ ├── 000000000001.jpg │ └── 000000000002.jpg └── val2017 └── 000000000001.jpg Convert coco_to_labelimg --data_dir dataset/YOLOV5_COCO_format --data_dir: the directory where the COCO format dataset is located. Default is dataset/YOLOV5_COCO_format. Converted directory structure (see dataset/COCO_labelImg_format for details): COCO_labelImg_format ├── train │ ├── 000000000001.
